    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      231.71,
      542.81,
      246.26
    ],
    "text": "The 4th Respondent was employed at the Petitioner Bank from 21.04.1992 to 30.11.2008. The",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      256.25,
      542.22,
      268.25
    ],
    "text": "subject matter of this application is the surcharge due on the delayed payment of gratuity to",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      275.66,
      255.84,
      290.21
    ],
    "text": "the 4th Respondent by the Petitioner.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      310.25,
      542.69,
      322.25
    ],
    "text": "The total due as gratuity is the sum of Rs. 39,47,200/=. A sum of Rs. 1,973,600/= was paid to",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      329.66,
      542.64,
      344.21
    ],
    "text": "the 4th Respondent on 15.05.2009, which is 50% of the total due, and the balance of Rs.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      354.17,
      505.49,
      366.17
    ],
    "text": "1,973,600/= was paid on 17.11.2009. The gratuity should have been paid on 30.12.2008.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      383.54,
      542.65,
      398.09
    ],
    "text": "The 4th Respondent made two complaints to the Commissioner-General of Labour, P4 and P9,",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      408.17,
      300.84,
      420.17
    ],
    "text": "claiming a surcharge for the delayed payment.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      440.11,
      542.5,
      452.11
    ],
    "text": "The first complaint P4 is dated 17.05.2010. The proceedings of the inquiry into this complaint",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      459.52,
      542.79,
      474.07
    ],
    "text": "are marked 1R1 to 1R3. A sum of Rs. 1,973,600/= was paid to the 4th Respondent on 15.05.2008",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      481.48,
      542.47,
      496.03
    ],
    "text": "as the 1st installment of the gratuity which is within the 6 months after the due date. Section",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      505.99,
      542.66,
      517.99
    ],
    "text": "5(4)(c) of the Payment of Gratuity Act No. 12 of 1983 (Act) as amended specifies that the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      527.95,
      542.47,
      539.95
    ],
    "text": "surcharge should be 20% of the sum due when the delay is between one to six months as in this",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      547.48,
      542.63,
      562.03
    ],
    "text": "case. Therefore, the surcharge due on the 1st installment of Rs. 1,973,600/= is Rs. 3,94,720/= as",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      571.99,
      176.01,
      583.99
    ],
    "text": "correctly calculated.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      603.94,
      542.81,
      615.94
    ],
    "text": "The 2nd complaint P9 is dated 17.11.2011. The proceedings of the inquiry into this complaint are",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      625.9,
      542.37,
      637.9
    ],
    "text": "marked 1R4 to 1R6. By P10 the Petitioner was directed to pay a sum of Rs. 493,000/= as",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      647.86,
      542.64,
      659.86
    ],
    "text": "surcharge for the delay in paying this second installment. This amount has been computed",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      669.82,
      542.58,
      681.82
    ],
    "text": "according to section 5(4)(d) of the Act which specifies a surcharge of 25% of the sum due when",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      731.26,
      542.6,
      755.74
    ],
    "text": "Page 4 of 4",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      74.42,
      542.28,
      86.42
    ],
    "text": "the delay is between six months to twelve months as in this case. Hence, the surcharge",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      96.38,
      351.5,
      108.38
    ],
    "text": "imposed by P10 is lawful and in accordance with the Act.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      128.42,
      542.59,
      140.42
    ],
    "text": "The Petitioner is seeking a writ of certiorari quashing P10. It is claimed that the Petitioner is not",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      150.38,
      542.79,
      162.38
    ],
    "text": "subject to section 10 of the Act. However, other than the mere ipse dixit, the Petitioner has not",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      172.34,
      542.78,
      184.34
    ],
    "text": "explained in the written submissions why the Petitioner is not caught up within section. A",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      194.3,
      508.97,
      206.3
    ],
    "text": "careful examination of section 10 of the Act establishes that it applies to every employer.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      223.67,
      542.67,
      238.22
    ],
    "text": "It was further submitted that the 3rd Respondent failed to appreciate that the Petitioner had",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      245.63,
      542.57,
      260.21
    ],
    "text": "made payment of terminal benefits to the 4th Respondent in excess of the amount legally due.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      270.29,
      542.29,
      282.29
    ],
    "text": "However, the Petitioner has failed to establish this position. In any event, it is irrelevant as the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      292.25,
      542.34,
      304.25
    ],
    "text": "issue is whether the gratuity was paid by the due date. Parties cannot by agreement exclude",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      314.21,
      542.72,
      326.21
    ],
    "text": "the application of the provisions of the Act. Undoubtedly there has been a delay in the payment",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      336.17,
      384.26,
      348.17
    ],
    "text": "of gratuity and the surcharge due has been properly calculated.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      365.54,
      542.81,
      380.09
    ],
    "text": "For all the foregoing reasons, the application is dismissed. The Petitioner shall pay the 4th",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      390.05,
      375.38,
      402.05
    ],
    "text": "Respondent a sum of Rs. 50,000/= as costs of this application.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      360.07,
      486.07,
      502.01,
      498.07
    ],
    "text": "Judge of the Court of Appeal",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
